# Role Mailer 0.5

This adds a tab at admin/content 'Role Mailer' where you can select Roles,
enter subject and a message and send them to all users of those roles. The
message and and subject are saved in case there are only minor changes to
each batch of email.

## Dependencies

- Drupal 7

